Conspiracy_Channels 

If you ever wish to talk to another member in the game in a private chat, then conspiracy channels is perfect for you. 
Use the command `!cc create <name> [members]` to create a "conspiracy channel", which is like a private chat but inside the game for anyone you wish. 
Note that each such channel costs 50 coins. Use !help cc to learn more about these commands.

Solos have the ability to create anonymous ccs with anyone in the game, these ccs will allow them to talk to a person anonymously. These are free but are created by the hosts.
